Date: September 10

To: Google, Inc.
Attn: Google Legal Support, AdSensc DMCA Complaints
[private] Fax Number: [private]

Subject: RE: [#177222569] Google AdSense DMCA complaint
Date: Sun, 9 Sep 2007 22:20:34 [#1772225691 Google AdSense DMCA
Complaint received email from Google Adsense requesting to resend fax with a new DMCA complaint with the URL displaying the allegedly
infringing material.
Date: Sun, 12 Aug 2007 09:22:20 replied to Adsense email stating www.eheepskinandthings.Com was available and advertising on their site email included attached photos of infringing material.
Date: August 8, 2007 12:07 PM [#1.17222569] Google AdSense DMCA
Complaint received email from Google Adsense stating they were unable to locate the allegedly infringing content. The site appears to be unavailable at tnis Linie.
Date: August B, 2007 DMCA complaint with the URL displaying the allegedly infringing material_

To whom It May concern,
